25|$|On 22 December 2014, Tepco crews {{completed}} {{the removal of}} all fuel assemblies, and the spent <b>fuel</b> <b>pool</b> of Reactor 4 no longer contained any stored fuel rods. The majority of the spent fuel assemblies were moved to the common spent <b>fuel</b> <b>pool</b> {{while some of the}} unused fuel assemblies were moved to the spent <b>fuel</b> <b>pool</b> of Unit 6.|$|E
